{"tid":874983,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"中國隊踢亞洲盃 舉行巴士標語公投","createTime":"2018-10-24T15:07:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T19:08:42.000Z","uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0e6865a72af12b92072c55ec27ce7bd28dd3cad0","tid":874983,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T15:07:22.000Z","msg":"2019年亞洲杯將於2019年1月5日至2月1日在阿聯酋舉行，隨著比賽時間越來越近，亞足聯官網也開設了&ldquo;球隊大巴標語投票活動&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據亞足聯官網的選項，中國國家隊的球隊大巴有三種標語可選：<br />\n<br />\n1.飛龍在天，中國驕傲<br />\n<br />\n2.勇氣、堅韌，攜手奮進<br />\n<br />\n3.為同一個夢想而戰<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得哪一個標語最棒，快戳鏈接投票吧！傳送門&gt;&gt;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.the-afc.com/competitions/afc-asian-cup/latest/news/vote-for-team-bus-slogan-group-c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.the-afc.com%2Fcompetitions%2Fafc-asian-cup%2Flatest%2Fnews%2Fvote-for-team-bus-slogan-group-c&d=3l%2FvdMGQVhuJuhsOpjTboZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=ac0e77f6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.the-afc.com/competitions/afc-asian-cup/latest/news/vote-for-team-bus-slogan-group-c</a>"},{"pid":"9ec3373ba0fada65d5ebd4e7e850506873ded80a","tid":874983,"uid":9230,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T15:10:34.000Z","msg":"打！往死裡打！"},{"pid":"4265e9018a9a704cfd39015c2de560d8184e561d","tid":874983,"uid":68215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T15:16:22.000Z","msg":"中國或成最大贏家"},{"pid":"011859b06970a9b8ad9dfe8eef98f4352b925bf6","tid":874983,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T15:22:07.000Z","msg":"納比睇黎要為左揾錢要臨老唔過得世"},{"pid":"3b21ad17e7d166134b61b9e5d9f81074b4f7f66a","tid":874983,"uid":8810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T16:25:08.000Z","msg":"四哥.jpg"},{"pid":"044c306db217b167d2604614c3652c083b87fa34","tid":874983,"uid":43809,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T16:27:35.000Z","msg":"功成不必在我"},{"pid":"aeacc989ebfbd10aa19a069049fc1ca8eb5f